{"tid":1393876,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【包生仔懶人教學】申請成為陪審員","createTime":"2019-08-01T08:33:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-04T09:47:16.000Z","uid":255155,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"32f34fd7d082e62e9bdaa2628d8a8d51ad9b38f5","tid":1393876,"uid":255155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T08:33:25.000Z","msg":"受阿叔 <span style=\"color: red;\">已戒瞓覺</span> 啟發，今日嘗試打電話去28254668 check自己係唔係個陪審員list度，相信係好多人都一齊打呢個電話，所以打勁多次先有職員接聽電話。<br />\n如果你未打或者打去冇人聽，請你不妨睇睇自己係咪同下面個case一樣：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1. 大學／大專畢業<br />\n2. 近呢幾年從未改過屋企地址<br />\n3. 從未收過有關成為陪審員嘅信件</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">＝ 你不在陪審員名單之中</span></span><br />\n<br />\n如果你中咗上面幾項，你可以打電話check嘅時間都慳返，直接做以下四步：<br />\n1. 寫封信表示你想做陪審員【參下文template】<br />\n2. 填好ROP18份表【參下文下載Link】<br />\n3. 你的畢業證書副本<br />\n4. 寄「香港灣仔告士打道七號入境事務大樓1201室陪審團登記小組」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">書信template：</span></strong></span><br />\n香港灣仔告士打道七號<br />\n入境事務大樓1201室<br />\n陪審團登記小組<br />\n執事先生鈞鑒：<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><ins>陪審員申請書</ins></div><br />\n<br />\n你好，本人於近日向主理陪審團事務書記辦事處查詢自己是否在陪審員名單，發現自己不在名單之中。然，出任陪審員乃是所有合乎資格的香港居民應盡之責。身為香港人，本人希望力盡公民責任，故特此函達申請成為陪審員。<br />\n<br />\n本人陳大文（Chan Tai Man），香港身份證號碼（A123456(7)），出生日期（04/06/1989），現申請成為陪審員，隨函附上表格ROP18及本人之最高學歷證明文件副本。如有任何查詢，歡迎致電1234-5678或電郵chantaiman@gmail.com與本人聯絡。謝謝。<br />\n<br />\n       敬祝<br />\n鈞祺<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\">＿＿＿＿＿＿＿（簽署）<br />\n陳大文謹啟</div><br />\n二零一九年八月一日<br />\n附件一：表格ROP18<br />\n附件二：最高學歷證明文件副本<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>ROP18表格下載Link</strong></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.immd.gov.hk/pdforms/rop18.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.immd.gov.hk%2Fpdforms%2Frop18.pdf&d=H0od%2FlU2Kx31F%2BxGtrrl5%2BrBpkLuHOqafswNxXmn3gI%3D&h=a4ce98ce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.immd.gov.hk/pdforms/rop18.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n附埋另一個關於陪審員post！<br />\n【一張圖睇晒】阿叔提提你，唔一定係要大學先做到陪審員！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1392543\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1392543</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"900ca46bf8a2e76202a691546b2711b56c3f6b9a","tid":1393876,"uid":255155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T08:34:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"480d5a9ffbdf92e3dac1418b6f02a56450a35e03","tid":1393876,"uid":255155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T08:35:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cf10189476e020fab5046ec72c8a006878e7d958","tid":1393876,"uid":255155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T08:37:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2a27865c123e86efd03983c8372bb6ef6e959bb5","tid":1393876,"uid":255155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T08:37:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e178364782544bb277358e5bd0ccbde7f53341b8","tid":1393876,"uid":255155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T08:39:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"03b327c522f85d6aeca60a34da6f5055e8b63e60","tid":1393876,"uid":282118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T08:41:29.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"cecd6c23eb8e298b65a2f86dd51d17cd56fd6403","tid":1393876,"uid":271857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T08:42:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fuKa4pDfCC8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DfuKa4pDfCC8&d=H0od%2FlU2Kx31F%2BxGtrrl5%2BrBpkLuHOqafswNxXmn3gI%3D&h=dcf6dd1d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fuKa4pDfCC8</a>"},{"pid":"39f0b98a84016856396dea0bd5533e34fff7fe9e","tid":1393876,"uid":255155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T08:47:19.000Z","msg":"唔好意思啊，第一次出post，我估我自己開錯台。我去時